@startuml
title TestForge v1 — C4 Context (codigo: 9 modulos, 1876 LOC, 93 testes)

!includeurl https://raw.githubusercontent.com/plantuml-stdlib/C4-PlantUML/master/C4_Context.puml

LAYOUT_WITH_LEGEND()

Person(qa, "QA Engineer", "Grava fluxos e recebe scripts com self-healing.")

System(testforge, "TestForge CLI", "Python CLI (Typer)\n9 modulos implementados")

System_Ext(web_app, "Aplicacao Web Alvo", "PrimeFaces, Angular, JSF, React")

System_Ext(llm, "LLM Gateway", "Opcional — off critical path")

Rel(qa, testforge, "Usa CLI", "record, run, compile")
Rel(testforge, web_app, "Playwright nativo", "page.on(), page.fill(), page.click()")
Rel(testforge, llm, "Consulta quando deterministico falha", "Prompt estruturado")

note right of testforge
  Implementado (v0.1.0):
  - recorder (JS injection)
  - evidence (JSONL store)
  - semantic (MIS + Compiler)
  - oracle (visual_dom + business_state)
  - promotion (Gate com 3 estados)
  - taxonomy (11 codigos, 6 familias)
  - runner (ShadowValidator + FallbackRunner)
  - metrics (precision, false_heal_rate)
  - cli (app.py)
end note

@enduml
